{"tid":1442713,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟爬山只係一個笑話","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T05:26:23.000Z","uid":77089,"like":26,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"73d2bfcb22434ba977b301f9e8dc451fcfe16ae1","tid":1442713,"uid":77089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:44:03.000Z","msg":"唔係標題黨 事實真係咁<br />\n琴日有機場有大埔<br />\n點解要叫人去機場唔好去大埔<br />\n係唔係好似選舉咁 當你出一個候選人 就應該講埋有邊D同區候選人<br />\n今日有深水埗 有北角<br />\n係咁叫人唔好去北角 去深水埗 <br />\n咩叫兄弟爬山?一定要跟你?<br />\n麻煩以後 唔好講唔好去邊<br />\n要講就講當日有邊D地方可以去 <br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">好似話去北角可以證明俾大家地香港係香港人嘅 香港人去邊就去邊 自己地方唔通要怕外人?</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>去深水埗 可以話係支持激光教港 聲援浸大學生</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">至少你要兩邊列曬 等人自己決定 唔係叫人去曬一個地方 唔去就話鬼話分化</span>"},{"pid":"817437e5739f2a9107d2053f8d8a62479307e621","tid":1442713,"uid":273272,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"宜家起緊大台呀，你咪出嚟分化好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n北角見。"},{"pid":"9ae6520bd4670a22e265878447ad5bfa4826cdd4","tid":1442713,"uid":77089,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"817437e5739f2a9107d2053f8d8a62479307e621","tid":1442713,"uid":273272,"like":1,"dislike":12,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:46:05.000Z","msg":"宜家起緊大台呀，你咪出嚟分化好唔好？<br />\n<br />\n北角見。"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:47:07.000Z","msg":"講D你唔想聽嘅事實就分化?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"107dd6e19250f4f25f9f3d7886091f2e204d060f","tid":1442713,"uid":77089,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:48:08.000Z","msg":"連出現左咩問題都唔面對 講個問題出來就叫分化?<br />\n<br />\n出緊北角<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c286b928bac72aef1c33d05ac2260fb51b766e00","tid":1442713,"uid":147721,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime